full_text: Case 1:20-cr-00330-PAE Document 216 Filed 04/19/21 Page 2 of 2 If the Government does not intend to use any of the documents subject to the pending motions to suppress in the trial of the non-perjury counts, the Court will defer consideration of those motions until it has scheduled the trial of the perjury counts. SO ORDERED. Dated: April 19, 2021 New York, New York Alison J. Nathan United States District Judge 2 DOJ-OGR-00003846
